 with the SN or a young stellar\ncluster that could host a massive WR progenitor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2013 22:07:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 16:12:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
