ch requires high computational resources and long\nrunning time on a supercomputer even for bacterial genome datasets, our\nsoftware can produce comparable assembly using only a standard desktop in a\nshort running time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2013 12:05:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-31"}
