a}-myrcene, limonene and 3-octanone. This study\nconstitutes the first comprehensive analysis of the headspace volatiles emitted\nfrom Physarum Polycephalum. Further work to understand the origin and function\nof the volatiles identified is required.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2013 15:36:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-31"}
